com.uber.rxdogtag.autodispose

Class AutoDisposeObserverHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.uber.rxdogtag.autodispose.AutoDisposeObserverHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.uber.rxdogtag.ObserverHandler

    public class AutoDisposeObserverHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.uber.rxdogtag.ObserverHandler
    A ObserverHandler that supports handling AutoDispose's decorating observers to retrieve their underlying delegate observers.

    Usage: Add INSTANCE to the list of SubscribeHandlers in RxDogTag.install(List).
